about.summary: Helper functions, etc. for the Python `logging` module

name: logging-helpers
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "logging-helpers" %}
{% set version = "0.4.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/sci-bots/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0c42b69ac62650257dd189258b32be0c357492b6e17eea13e087a885dfbd8550

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - logging_helpers

about:
  home: http://github.com/sci-bots/{{ name }}
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: 'Helper functions, etc. for the Python `logging` module'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cfobel
